<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home - Futuristic Translator</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #222831, #393e46);
      color: #eeeeee;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: #00adb5;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    /* Section Styles */
    section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 1200px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #222831, #393e46);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    section h1, section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #00adb5;
    }

    section p {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #eeeeee;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero-section {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-section .button-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* Button Styles */
    .dialog-button {
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #222831;
      background-color: #00adb5;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .dialog-button:hover {
      background-color: #00ffcb;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Features Section */
    .features-section ul {
      margin: 20px auto 0;
      padding: 0;
      max-width: 800px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .features-section ul li {
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #393e46;
    }

    /* Dashboard Section */
    .dashboard-container {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .dashboard-container .button-container {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    /* Subscription Table */
    .subscription-table {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .subscription-table th, .subscription-table td {
      border: 1px solid #00adb5;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subscription-table th {
      background-color: #393e46;
      color: #00adb5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .subscription-table td {
      background-color: #222831;
      color: #eeeeee;
    }

    .subscription-table tr:hover {
      background-color: #393e46;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <h1>Welcome to Robo Uni-Translator</h1>
    <p>Translate your text accurately and efficiently, breaking language barriers around the world.</p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="/signup" class="dialog-button">Sign Up</a>
      <a href="/login" class="dialog-button">Log In</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <h2>Why Choose Robo Uni Translator?</h2>
    <p>Our advanced translation service offers fast, accurate, and reliable translations for over 100 languages. Whether you're a business, traveler, or student, we ensure you communicate effortlessly with anyone around the globe.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for over 6 languages and Unicode</li>
      <li>Accurate translations with contextual understanding</li>
      <li>Real-time translations for conversations and texts</li>
      <li>Available on desktop and mobile for seamless use</li>
      <li>User-friendly interface with a clean, intuitive design</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Dashboard Section -->
  <section class="dashboard-container">
    <h1>Your Translation Dashboard</h1>
    <p>Track your translation history, access premium features, and manage your subscription all in one place.</p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="/dashboard" class="dialog-button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Subscription Section -->
  <section class="dashboard-container">
    <h1>Subscription Plans</h1>
    <p>Select the plan that best suits your needs. We offer flexible pricing options to meet the requirements of every user, from casual users to businesses with high-volume translation needs.</p>
    <table class="subscription-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Plan</th>
          <th>Features</th>
          <th>Price</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Basic</td>
          <td>Unlimited translations, 24/7 support</td>
          <td>$5/month</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Pro</td>
          <td>All Basic features + Real-time conversation translations</td>
          <td>$15/month</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Business</td>
          <td>All Pro features + Custom integrations and API access</td>
          <td>$50/month</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
